♪You have wide shoulders♪

145
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:38,840
♪Protecting me from the rain and wind♪

146
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:42,120
♪Keeping you company is an honour♪

147
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:45,440
♪In this long journey♪

148
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:51,040
♪Love is shining gently♪

149
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:54,880
♪In our eyes♪

150
